# airbyte_source_spacex_api (Resource)

SourceSpacexAPI Resource

## Example Usage

```terraform

  configuration = {
    id      = "e45dfad9-324f-46ab-9f83-34526eae71eb"
    options = "...my_options..."
  }
  definition_id = "759d7dd0-bf2f-4572-9957-8fbbe9226a95"
  name          = "Elisa Wunsch"
  secret_id     = "...my_secret_id..."

}
```
